  "texts": [
    "After segmenting the corpus into individual sentences, the dataset still contains entries that do not constitute genuine sentences of the primary text.",
    "Instead, these entries include tables, annotations, or binary data erroneously recognized as text during the PDF conversion process.",
    "To address this issue, we implement conservative rules aimed at filtering out clearly irrelevant entries:",
    "• Remove sentences with less than 2/3 ASCII characters • Remove sentences that consists of less than 6 tokens or more than 200 tokens • Remove sentences with less than 20 characters After pre-processing, we obtain a dataset that consists of 2,034,313 sentences.",
    "A small share of sentences do not contain relevant text, i.e., some chart annotations, references etc. remain."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}